texts.content: {"text":"1. Osmonlaru yerdagi barcha narsalar \nAllohga tasbih aytadi. \nU zot g`olib va hikmat egasidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,94]}]}

{"text":"2. Ey, iymon keltirganlar! \nNima uchun qilmagan narsalaringizni gapirasiz?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,75]}]}

{"text":"3. Qilmaydigan narsangizni gapirishingiz \nAllohning nazdida qattiq yomon ko`rilgandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,86]}]}

{"text":"4. Albatta, Alloh O`z yo`lida xuddi jips binodek bo`lib, safda turib urush qiladiganlarni yaxshi ko`radir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,106]}]}

{"text":"5. Muso o`z qavmiga: «Ey qavmim, \nAllohning Rasuli ekanimni bilib turib yana nima uchun menga ozor berasiz», deganini esla. \nUlar (haqdan) burilgan edilar, Alloh ularning qalbini burib qo`ydi. Alloh fosiq qavmlarni hidoyat qilmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,230]}]}

{"text":"6. Iyso ibn Maryam: «Ey, Bani Isroil, albatta, \nmen o`zimdan oldin kelgan Tavrotni tasdiqlash \nva mendan keyin keluvchi Ahmad ismli Rasulning bashoratini berish uchun Alloh sizlarga yuborgan Payg`ambarman», deganini esla. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,222]}]}

{"text":"Qachonki u(Ahmad) ularga haq bilan \nkelgan vaqtda esa, bu ochiq-oydin sehrdir, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,87]}]}

{"text":"7. Islomga da'vat qilinib turganida 
Allohga nisbatan yolg`on to`qigan 
kimsadan ham zolimroq kishi bormi? 
Holbuki, Alloh zolimlarni hidoyatga solmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,151]}]}

{"text":"8. Og`izlari bilan Allohning nurini 
o`chirmoqchi bo`ladilar. 
Holbuki, Alloh, kofirlar yoqtirmasa ham, 
o`z nurini tugal etguvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,134]}]}

{"text":"9. U zot O`z Rasulini hidoyat va haq din bilan barcha dinlardan ustun qilish uchun yuborgan Zotdir. Garchi mushriklar yoqtirmasalar ham.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,136]}]}

{"text":"10. Ey, iymon keltirganlar! Sizlarni alamli azobdan najot toptiruvchi tijoratga dalolat qilaymi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,96]}]}

{"text":"11. Allohga va Uning Rasuliga iymon keltirasizlar hamda Uning yo`lida molingiz va joningiz bilan jihod qilasizlar. Shundoq qilmoqlaringiz, agar bilsangizlar, o`zlaringiz uchun yaxshidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,186]}]}

{"text":"12. Gunohlaringizni kechirur va sizlarni adn jannatidagi (daraxtlari) ostidan anhorlar oqib turgan bog`larga va yaxshi maskanlarga kiritur. \nBu narsa siz uchun ulug` yutuqdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,175]}]}

{"text":"13. Va sizlar yaxshi ko`radigan boshqasi ham bor. Allohdan yordam va yaqin zafar. \nVa mo`minlarga bashorat ber.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"14. Ey, iymon keltirganlar! 
Allohning yordamchilari bo`ling! 
Iyso ibn Maryam havoriylarga: 
«Kim Alloh uchun mening yordamchim(bo`ladi)?» deganida, havoriylar: ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,162]}]}

{"text":"«Biz Allohning yordamchilarimiz», dedilar. \nBas, Bani Isroildan bir toifa iymon keltirdi va bir toifa kofir bo`ldi. Bas, Biz iymon keltirganlarni dushmanlari ustidan qo`llab-quvvatladik. Va ular g`olib bo`ldilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,212]}]}

{"text":"سَبَّحَ لِلَّهِ مَا فِى ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَمَا فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ ۖ\n وَهُوَ ٱلْعَزِيزُ ٱلْحَكِيمُ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,89]}]}

{"text":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ لِمَ تَقُولُونَ مَا لَا تَفْعَلُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,69]}]}

{"text":"كَبُرَ مَقْتًا عِندَ ٱللَّهِ أَن تَقُولُوا۟ مَا لَا تَفْعَلُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,63]}]}

{"text":"إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ يُحِبُّ ٱلَّذِينَ يُقَٰتِلُونَ فِى سَبِيلِهِۦ صَفًّۭا كَأَنَّهُم بُنْيَٰنٌۭ مَّرْصُوصٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,101]}]}

{"text":"وَإِذْ قَالَ مُوسَىٰ لِقَوْمِهِۦ يَٰقَوْمِ لِمَ تُؤْذُونَنِى وَقَد تَّعْلَمُونَ أَنِّى رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ إِلَيْكُمْ ۖ\n فَلَمَّا زَاغُوٓا۟ أَزَاغَ ٱللَّهُ قُلُوبَهُمْ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ لَا يَهْدِى ٱلْقَوْمَ ٱلْفَٰسِقِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,211]}]}

{"text":"وَإِذْ قَالَ عِيسَى ٱبْنُ مَرْيَمَ يَٰبَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ إِنِّى رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ إِلَيْكُم مُّصَدِّقًۭا لِّمَا \nبَيْنَ يَدَىَّ مِنَ ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ وَمُبَشِّرًۢا بِرَسُولٍۢ يَأْتِى مِنۢ بَعْدِى ٱسْمُهُۥٓ أَحْمَدُ ۖ ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,214]}]}

{"text":"فَلَمَّا جَآءَهُم بِٱلْبَيِّنَٰتِ قَالُوا۟ هَٰذَا سِحْرٌۭ مُّبِينٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"وَمَنْ أَظْلَمُ مِمَّنِ ٱفْتَرَىٰ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ ٱلْكَذِبَ وَهُوَ يُدْعَىٰٓ إِلَى ٱلْإِسْلَٰمِ ۚ \nوَٱللَّهُ لَا يَهْدِى ٱلْقَوْمَ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,142]}]}

{"text":"يُرِيدُونَ لِيُطْفِـُٔوا۟ نُورَ ٱللَّهِ بِأَفْوَٰهِهِمْ وَٱللَّهُ مُتِمُّ نُورِهِۦ وَلَوْ كَرِهَ ٱلْكَٰفِرُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,110]}]}

{"text":"هُوَ ٱلَّذِىٓ أَرْسَلَ رَسُولَهُۥ بِٱلْهُدَىٰ وَدِينِ ٱلْحَقِّ لِيُظْهِرَهُۥ عَلَى ٱلدِّينِ كُلِّهِۦ \nوَلَوْ كَرِهَ ٱلْمُشْرِكُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,130]}]}

{"text":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ هَلْ أَدُلُّكُمْ عَلَىٰ تِجَٰرَةٍۢ تُنجِيكُم مِّنْ عَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍۢ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,101]}]}

{"text":"تُؤْمِنُونَ بِٱللَّهِ وَرَسُولِهِۦ وَتُجَٰهِدُونَ فِى سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ بِأَمْوَٰلِكُمْ وَأَنفُسِكُمْ ۚ \nذَٰلِكُمْ خَيْرٌۭ لَّكُمْ إِن كُنتُمْ تَعْلَمُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,152]}]}

{"text":"يَغْفِرْ لَكُمْ ذُنُوبَكُمْ وَيُدْخِلْكُمْ جَنَّٰتٍۢ تَجْرِى مِن تَحْتِهَا ٱلْأَنْهَٰرُ \nوَمَسَٰكِنَ طَيِّبَةًۭ فِى جَنَّٰتِ عَدْنٍۢ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلْفَوْزُ ٱلْعَظِيمُ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,163]}]}

{"text":"وَأُخْرَىٰ تُحِبُّونَهَا ۖ نَصْرٌۭ مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ وَفَتْحٌۭ قَرِيبٌۭ ۗ وَبَشِّرِ ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,94]}]}

{"text":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ كُونُوٓا۟ أَنصَارَ ٱللَّهِ كَمَا قَالَ عِيسَى \nٱبْنُ مَرْيَمَ لِلْحَوَارِيِّۦنَ مَنْ أَنصَارِىٓ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ ۖ ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,146]}]}

{"text":"قَالَ ٱلْحَوَارِيُّونَ نَحْنُ أَنصَارُ ٱللَّهِ ۖ فَـَٔامَنَت طَّآئِفَةٌۭ مِّنۢ بَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ \nوَكَفَرَت طَّآئِفَةٌۭ ۖ فَأَيَّدْنَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ عَلَىٰ عَدُوِّهِمْ فَأَصْبَحُوا۟ ظَٰهِرِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,204]}]}

{"text":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,0.74901962280273438,0.45098039507865906]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":14,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,40]}]}

{"text":"Mehribon va rahmli \nAllohning nomi bilan boshlayman","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/CapCut/User Data/Cache/effect/7202912523383738881/62f9677bff07407d954efbb810d8273e/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":"7202912523383738881"},"size":10,"range":[0,51]}]}
